    <item>
      <title>选民前往投票站时巴基斯坦暂停移动电话服务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/pakistan-stops-mobile-phone-services-nationwide-on-election-day</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，选民在大选中排队投票时，巴基斯坦暂停了移动电话服务，并辩称该措施是维持秩序的一种方式，尽管批评者称这将限制在有争议的民意调查期间获取重要信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/pakistan-stops-mobile-phone-services-nationwide-on-election-day</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 03:09:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党将放弃英国280亿英镑的绿色投资目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/labour-to-announce-shift-on-28-billion-green-investment-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工党领袖凯尔·斯塔默(Keir Starmer)预计将放弃其280亿英镑(350亿美元)的绿色投资承诺，此前数周的内部争论是否因预算问题而取消这一旗舰政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/labour-to-announce-shift-on-28-billion-green-investment-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 21:41:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国在巴格达无人机袭击中杀死伊朗支持的民兵领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/us-kills-commander-of-iran-backed-militiant-group-in-iraq-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三晚上，美国在巴格达发动无人机袭击，杀死了伊朗支持的民兵指挥官，白宫将目标锁定为上个月对美国基地发动致命袭击的组织。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/us-kills-commander-of-iran-backed-militiant-group-in-iraq-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 21:14:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黑莉否认内华达州失利，称特朗普的初选程序被“操纵”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/haley-dismisses-nevada-primary-loss-calling-process-rigged-for-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼基·黑利(Nikki Haley)否认了内华达州共和党总统初选中令人尴尬的失利，称该州的提名程序被“操纵”，有利于竞争对手唐纳德·特朗普(Donald Trump)，并批评他对党的控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/haley-dismisses-nevada-primary-loss-calling-process-rigged-for-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 19:39:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
